                     \<action=`pavucontrol` button=1><action=`xdotool key XF86AudioRaiseVolume` button=4><action=`xdotool key XF86AudioLowerVolume` button=5>Vol: %VolumePipe%</action></action></action> | \
                     \<action=`xdotool key XF86MonBrightnessUp` button=4><action=`xdotool key XF86MonBrightnessDown` button=5>Bright: %BrightPipe%</action></action> | \
